Use SDFrame as a public, read-only software design framework reference.

Repository rules:
- Prefer small, factual edits that preserve the generated catalog structure.
- Regenerate public assets with `node scripts/generate-all.js` after data or generator changes.
- Verify with `npm run build`.
- Keep machine-readable agent files truthful. Do not claim private accounts, paid plans, OAuth, SDKs, CLI tools, registry listings, or live MCP/WebMCP support unless those actually exist.
- Link agents to `SKILL.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `llms.txt`, `llms-full.txt`, `/openapi.json`, and `/api/frameworks.index.json`.

